"useful and accurate estimates of hourly and daily PM2.5 concentrations at a regulatory monitoring site by combining one such sensor with other low-cost, readily available hardware. Guided by the prior work of Watson, Wilson, Chow and colleagues (Watson, 2002; Watson et al., 1998; Wilson et al., 2002, 2005; Wilson and Suh, 1997)," (Holstius et al 2014:1122)
