"We are apparently the first to evaluate such a sensor under ambient conditions at a US regulatory monitoring site, and the first to calibrate it using 24 h averages of PM2.5 from a reference instrument with Federal Equivalent Method (FEM) status" (Holstius et al 2014:1122)},
